OL,3,CBristol mother joins forces with
OL,4,Cpolice to tackle drug driving
OL,6,FDaniel Davies had recently celebrated
OL,7,Fhis 16th birthday when he died on 17
OL,8,FApril 2022.
OL,10,FHarry Charlton, 29, has been jailed
OL,11,Ffor five years for causing his death
OL,12,Fby careless driving while over the
OL,13,Fprescribed limit of drugs.
OL,15,FThe court heard how he drove through a
OL,16,Fred light at the through-about
OL,17,Fjunction near Warmley and hit Daniel,
OL,18,Fwho was driving his moped.
