OL,6,FWhen he was tested, Charlton was found
OL,7,Fto be just over the legal limit for
OL,8,Fcannabis.
OL,10,FDaniel died at the scene after
OL,11,Fsuffering a head injury.
OL,13,FDaniel's mother Samantha still
OL,14,Fremembers that day like it was
OL,15,Fyesterday. She said: "I can remember
OL,16,Fwalking to the ring road. I walked up
OL,17,Fto Daniel and he was laying on the
OL,18,Fground with a white sheet over him.
