OL,6,F"I got down on the floor, I just put
OL,7,Fmy hands on his face and just spoke to
OL,8,Fhim."
OL,10,FDaniel's story is now part of a police
OL,11,Fcampaign highlighting the danger of
OL,12,Fdrug driving.
OL,14,FDuring December, Avon and Somerset
OL,15,FPolice made 241 arrests for driving
OL,16,Funder the influence of drink and/or
OL,17,Fdrugs as part of Operation Limit.
OL,19,FDrink driving accounted for 62% of
OL,20,Farrests, while drug driving offences
OL,21,Faccounted for 38% of arrests.
