OL,4,Cpolice to tackle drug driving
OL,6,FInspector Matt Boiles said: "The
OL,7,Fimpacts of drug driving are really
OL,8,Fsignificant. On a person we catch
OL,9,Fyou're looking at a prison sentence,
OL,10,Ffine or disqualification.
OL,12,F"In terms of the risk to other members
OL,13,Fof the public it increases your chance
OL,14,Fof being involved in a serious
OL,15,Fcollision which puts other people at
OL,16,Frisk of harm, serious injury or even
OL,17,Fdeath."
