OL,6,FSince the start of last year 55 fatal
OL,7,Fand serious injury collisions in the
OL,8,FAvon and Somerset Police force area
OL,9,Fhave been linked to drink or drug
OL,10,Fdriving.
OL,12,FSamantha said: "It's a mind-altering
OL,13,Fthing - so how can you safely be in
OL,14,Fcontrol of a car if you've taken
OL,15,Fsomething mind-changing.
OL,17,F"I think a lot of people smoke
OL,18,Fcannabis and it wouldn't surprise me
OL,19,Fif they think it's fine and just drive.
